\v 40 \x * \xo 25:40 \xt Pro 19:17; Mt 10:42, 18:5; Mk 9:41\x*‚ÄúTe hi M…®t…®k Iuwe ewenhi etpor, ‚ÄòHi hetpi werek. W…® kerek yi epei y…®kaap m…®t nai yinan in kerek nises h…®m mai, h…®ram mar ke yi yerekyewem.‚Äô
